description.narrative: Programme Coordination, which contributes to Technical Excellence In Policy And Programmes. title.narrative: Programme Coordination

description.narrative: Improved performance of budget and partnership management, while ensuring that programme assurance activities were undertaken ensured that programmes were implemented in a timely manner while mitigating and managing risks including the COVID-19. More staff and partners are aware of UNICEF policies, procedures and programme assurance ensuring HACT compliance rates of 102 percent of spot checks, 125 percent of programmatic visits, 24 Micro Assessments and 15 Audits.The use of eTools ensured better monitoring and management of implementing partners and the related programme assurance activities, including introduction of the Third Party Monitoring module and continued use of Trip Module. | Status:Partially met | As-of Date:18/01/2022
